{N\choose 0}a^N+{N\choose 1}a^{N-2}+{N\choose 2}a^{N-4}+{N\choose 3}a^{N-6}+\dots = \frac{a^2+1}{a}
\binom{N}{N}
\binom{N}{k}
k\gt N
\begin{align*} \binom{N}{0}a^N &+ \binom{N}{1}a^{N-2} + \cdots + \binom{N}{N}a^{N-2N}\\ &\qquad= \binom{N}{0}a^N\left(\frac{1}{a}\right)^0 + \binom{N}{1}a^{N-1}\left(\frac{1}{a}\right)^1 + \cdots + \binom{N}{N}a^0\left(\frac{1}{a}\right)^N.\end{align*}
\left(a+\frac{1}{a}\right)^N = \left(\frac{a^2+1}{a}\right)^N
N
